# Decay file for D0 Flow and Spin Alignment Studies
# -----------------------------------------------

# Define D*+ -> D0 pi+ (Vector to Scalar Scalar)
# This model naturally handles polarization if the parent is polarized.
Decay D*+
  1.0  D0  pi+         VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay D*-

# Define D0 -> K- pi+ (Scalar to Scalar Scalar)
Decay D0
  1.0  K-  pi+         PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-D0

End
